{"tid":1830974,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"政府收稅係咪唔可以收稅成本高過稅收","createTime":"2020-01-20T04:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T08:33:04.000Z","uid":117332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4bb802e391893922beea5c62864041bfc62b43e","tid":1830974,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"Dse既經濟學既principle of taxation就話稅收要最少費用，即係收稅既成本應該低，而且唔可以高過稅既revenue。<br />\n<br />\n我想問有無exception 同埋呢個principle係咪咁廣泛受接受。<br />\n<br />\n因為我就咁諗，稅既然已經有再分配既效果，如果佢目的在於再分配，就算佢turn out係蝕咗都可能被接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93355654d9f1e5fbc26e9f541f0b5fa9409260a5","tid":1830974,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:18:42.000Z","msg":"成本高過稅收 即係政府收完仲少錢咗 <br />\n<br />\n咁不如唔收，其他開支照舊"},{"pid":"336bd4104c8418e20bb11e2b6d019f65bd1e0215","tid":1830974,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93355654d9f1e5fbc26e9f541f0b5fa9409260a5","tid":1830974,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:18:42.000Z","msg":"成本高過稅收 即係政府收完仲少錢咗 <br />\n<br />\n咁不如唔收，其他開支照舊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"有時收稅唔係要賺錢架嘛<br />\n例如膠袋徵費每個袋收$0.5你估真係吼住舊錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}